      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both reliability and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure optimal mechanical performance and structural integrity. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a superior driving experience for the discerning motorist. We invite you to experience the caliber of this exceptional motorcar firsthand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, with just the typical character you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s actually been enjoyed! It\u2019s been well-loved, runs like a dream, and is ready for many more adventures. If you\u2019re looking for something reliable that still looks fantastic in the driveway, you've found it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 era. The powertrain features individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivering a linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed through a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal traction. Preventive maintenance is a priority here; the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells and the throttle actuators have been upgraded to address common failure points. The chassis retains its structural integrity, featuring the weight-saving carbon fiber roof and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable damping rates. While showing minor cosmetic signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and suspension geometry remain precise.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a reliable and refined driving experience. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, complemented by clean alloys and tires with plenty of tread remaining; while a few minor surface marks exist, they do not detract from its impressive curb appeal. Step inside to a cabin that feels fresh and inviting, featuring plush, well-preserved seating and a dashboard free of sun damage or cracks. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is robust\u2014the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. Backed by a consistent service history, this car represents a fantastic value for someone seeking luxury and longevity without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard. It exhibits consistent mechanical reliability and a refined exterior, offering a superior driving experience for the discerning professional. This offering represents a commitment to quality and serves as a reliable asset for its next owner. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the integrity of this well-preserved machine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It\u2019s been such a great car for me\u2014really smooth on the road and super dependable. It's in solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can just jump in and go! It's perfect for anyone who wants a quality car that's ready for its next adventure. I'd love for you to come by and take it for a spin\u2014feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and essential rear subframe reinforcement to address common chassis fatigue points. The suspension retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry, offering the precise turn-in and lateral stability enthusiasts demand. While the exterior shows minor evidence of spirited road use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all cylinders and cooling system integrity\u2014remain within tight tolerances. A driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
